Name                          Purpose                                                           Java pattern or principle included
MessagingFacade               Public entry point to the messaging subsystem; coordinates        Facade, Single responsibility
                              validation, routing and sending

SendResult                    Represents the result of a send operation, including response     Single responsibility
                              code, message text, provider used, channels tried and total cost

MessageSenderFactory          Creates concrete message sender instances for each channel        Factory, Open/Closed principle
                              and provider (e.g. SMS, Email, Postal)

MoneyFactory                  Creates Money value objects in specific currencies for senders    Factory, Single responsibility

RoutingPolicy                 Encapsulates routing rules; decides the preferred order of        Single responsibility, Open/Closed principle
                              channels and providers based on message type and urgency

ChainBuilder                  Builds the chain of responsibility using RoutingPolicy and        Chain of Responsibility, Factory, Single responsibility
                              MessageSenderFactory

IMessageSender                Interface for all message senders in the chain                    Single responsibility, Open/Closed principle

BaseSender                    Abstract base class implementing common chain behaviour           Chain of Responsibility, Single responsibility
                              (holding next sender, channel and cost)

TwilioSMSSender               Concrete SMS sender using the Twilio provider (stubbed with       Single responsibility, Open/Closed principle, Chain of Responsibility
                              System.out.println and simulated failures/costs)

CSoftSMSSender                Concrete SMS sender using the CSoft provider (stubbed with        Single responsibility, Open/Closed principle, Chain of Responsibility
                              System.out.println and simulated failures/costs)

SendGridEmailSender           Concrete email sender using a SendGrid-like provider (stubbed     Single responsibility, Open/Closed principle, Chain of Responsibility
                              with System.out.println and simulated failures/costs)

SESEmailSender                Concrete email sender using an SES-like provider (stubbed with    Single responsibility, Open/Closed principle, Chain of Responsibility
                              System.out.println and simulated failures/costs)

RoyalMailPostalSender         Concrete postal sender using a RoyalMail-like provider (stubbed   Single responsibility, Open/Closed principle, Chain of Responsibility
                              with System.out.println and simulated failures/costs)

RNGPostalSender               Concrete postal sender that randomly fails to demonstrate         Single responsibility, Open/Closed principle, Chain of Responsibility
                              fallback handling and cost calculation

User                          Models an application user and aggregates all contact details     Single responsibility
                              (email, phone number, postal address)

ContactDetails                Interface for user contact detail value objects                   Single responsibility, Open/Closed principle

EmailAddress                  Value object representing an email address                        Single responsibility

PhoneNumber                   Value object representing a phone number                          Single responsibility

PostalAddress                 Value object representing a postal address                        Single responsibility

Message                       Base class for messages to be sent with id, subject, content      Single responsibility, Open/Closed principle
                              and channel

SMSMessage                    Concrete message type representing an SMS message                 Single responsibility, Open/Closed principle

EmailMessage                  Concrete message type representing an email message               Single responsibility, Open/Closed principle

PostalMessage                 Concrete message type representing a postal/letter message        Single responsibility, Open/Closed principle

Channel                       Enum listing supported delivery channels                          Single responsibility

MessageType                   Enum representing logical types of messages (OTP, marketing,      Single responsibility
                              transactional, generic)

Urgency                       Enum representing urgency levels to influence routing             Single responsibility

Provider                      Enum listing concrete sender providers used by the system         Single responsibility

ResponseCode                  Enum describing possible outcomes of sending operations           Single responsibility

ContactValidator              Coordinates validation of a Userâ€™s contact details using          Single responsibility
                              specialised validators

EmailValidator                Validates the format of email addresses                           Single responsibility

PhoneValidator                Validates the format of phone numbers                             Single responsibility

PostcodeValidator             Validates the format of postal codes                              Single responsibility

IValidator                    Generic validator interface for contact detail objects            Single responsibility

ValidationReport              Collects validation errors and reports overall validity           Single responsibility

Money                         Represents monetary values with currency and arithmetic           Single responsibility

UUIDHandler                   Utility for generating and validating UUID identifiers            Single responsibility

MessagingException            Base runtime exception type for messaging errors                  Single responsibility

ValidationException           Exception for validation failures                                 Single responsibility

Main                          Program entry point; constructs the facade and dependencies       Uses Facade, exercises Factory and
                              and runs scenarios to test all features of the messaging system   Chain of Responsibility, demonstrates SRP/OCP
